00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:40.500
I was doing something called
ski touring in Italy, which

00:00:40.500 --> 00:00:44.625
is a strange, rather silly sport
where you walk up for six hours

00:00:44.625 --> 00:00:46.830
and you ski down for an hour.

00:00:46.830 --> 00:00:48.600
And it's very tiring.

00:00:48.600 --> 00:00:51.260
And that last day, and I
was really not feeling well,

00:00:51.260 --> 00:00:53.250
