00:00:53.250 --> 00:00:56.910
And I thought, oh, this is
just the end of a long week.

00:00:56.910 --> 00:00:57.750
Got to the bottom.

00:00:57.750 --> 00:00:59.520
And I had double vision.

00:00:59.520 --> 00:01:02.760
And this persisted.

00:01:02.760 --> 00:01:06.840
And being a medical doctor,
